  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></p><p>▪ Answer enquiries to customers by telephone call / text or email.</p><p>▪ Telemarketing - conduct outbound calls to potential customers, and following up on leads.</p><p>▪ Prepare and generate quotation, delivery order and invoice.</p><p>▪ Liaise and coordinate with clients to ensure timely delivery of goods.</p><p>▪ Process sales order and follow up payment with clients.</p><p>▪ Coordination, monitor and troubleshooting assistance for client’s order & account status.</p><p>▪ Ad-hoc duties as and when required.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements :</strong><br /><br />- Diploma or equivalent.</p><p>- With 1 – 2 years of relevant experience.</p><p>- Experience in telemarketing, sales & customer service is required.</p><p>- Proactive and positive working attitude.</p><p>- Meticulous with good organizational skills.</p><p>- Good interpersonal skills and able to work independently with minimum supervision.</p><p>- Ability to multi tasks and work under pressure.</p><p>- Proficient in MS Office.</p><p>- 5.5 days on Alternate Saturday.</p>",
